@bonsaixbt this is not to replace Claude or chatGPT. it’s for someone that don’t have $20 to pay for either or those providers.

the repo aggregate 14 different free tier model together, collectively giving you more that 1b LLM token to work with.

for more people, that’s enough for a month without hitting any rate limit

@tawer1O yeah

sticky sessions pin a chat to one provider for 30 min. 

if that one rate-limits or errors, the router falls down your fallback chain and replays the full message history to the next healthy model.
